com.spectralogic.ds3client.utils.collections

Interface LazyIterable.LazyLoaderFactory<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The model that is returned by the iterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GetBucketKeyLoaderFactory, GetBucketLoaderFactory, GetObjectsFullDetailsLoaderFactory
    Enclosing class:
    LazyIterable<T>

    public static interface LazyIterable.LazyLoaderFactory<T>
    A factory that creates instances of LazyLoaders. It's important that this factory does not return the same loader, otherwise every iterator created with this factory will share the same state and can lead to undefined behavior.
